macodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/298416/', '', 'Ezogabine, Lamotrigine, Ethosuximide, Lacosamide, Levetiracetam, Tiagabine, Ethotoin, Clonazepam, Paramethadione, Ganaxolone, Vigabatrin, More', 'Megestrol acetate, Estetrol, Megestrol acetate, Megestrol acetate', 1767369485);
